          </ParagraphSentence>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Hide="false" Num="3" OldStyle="false">
          <ParagraphNum>３</ParagraphNum>
          <ParagraphSentence>
            <Sentence WritingMode="vertical">施行日前作出的法律行为的成立、效力以及方式，作为新法第八条至第十二条规定的例外，仍依照此前的规定。</Sentence>
          </ParagraphSentence>
        </Paragraph>
        <Paragraph Hide="false" Num="4" OldStyle="false">
          <ParagraphNum>４</ParagraphNum>
          <ParagraphSentence>
